abstract: Evan Murray, quarterback for Warren Hills Regional High School in New Jersey, dies after sustaining injury during game against Summit High School; cause of death has not yet been determined.
lead_paragraph: Evan Murray, a three-sport athlete at Warren Hills Regional High School, was injured in a game against Summit High School on Friday night.

headline.main: High School Quarterback in New Jersey Dies After He Is Injured During a Game
